      "rationale": "Titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V modeled as bilinear isotropic hardening; material constants derived from tensile coupon data from the same lot as test constructs. Frictional contact (mu=0.3) at screw-rod interface validated against sub-component pull-out tests. Gradation 3 achieved."
