      "rationale": "Testing conducted under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration only. No alternative load configurations (e.g., torsion, axial compression alone) were included in this validation study. This limits condition coverage to Gradation 2, below the required Gradation 3. This shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given the direct correspondence between the test configuration and the COU loading scenario."
